column2: select p.objID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, z.p_cw, z.p_acw, z.spiral, p.deVAB_r, p.deVPhi_r, offsetRa_u, offsetRa_g, offsetRa_r, offsetRa_i, offsetRa_z, offsetDec_u, offsetDec_g, offsetDec_r, offsetDec_i, offsetDec_z from DR1#.zooSpec z join DR8.specObj s ON s.specObjID = z.specObjID join DR8.photoObj p ON p.objID = s.bestObjID join DR8.photoZ pz ON pz.objID = p.objID into mydb.zoo_offsets where (z.p_acw > = # or z.p_cw > = # or z.spiral > = #) and s.origObjId = s.bestObjId
